Gelf log enqueuer for greylog2

rewrite using gevent

- needs tweak on amqp pool
- would benefit of an internal backlog queue

test on MacOS X:

add this line to /etc/syslog.conf

*.notice;authpriv,remoteauth,ftp,install,internal.none  @127.0.0.1:8000         

restart syslogd:

launchctl unload /System/Library/LaunchDaemons/com.apple.syslogd.plist
launchctl load /System/Library/LaunchDaemons/com.apple.syslogd.plist

running: 

LOGIX_CONF=src/etc/logix.conf src/bin/logix &
LOGIX_CONF=src/etc/logix.conf src/bin/consumer.py &

logger test
